# ShiftSync Environment Variables

# OpenAI API Key for Schema Matching
# Create an account at https://platform.openai.com/
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# (Optional) If you want to use Anthropic or Gemini,
# you will need to swap out the logic in app/api/map/route.ts
# and add your respective keys here:
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant...
